1. Kada *ponudiš* posao, budi siguran da su svi detalji jasni. (When you offer a job, make sure all the details are clear.)
2. Nadamo se da će nam restoran *ponuditi* ukusna jela. (We hope the restaurant will offer us delicious food.)
3. Rekao sam mu da ću mu *ponuditi* pomoć ako mu bude potrebna. (I told him I would offer him help if he needs it.)
4. *Ponuda* koju smo dobili za novu kuću nije bila zadovoljavajuća. (The offer we received for the new house was not satisfactory.)
5. Odlučio sam *ponuditi* mu prijedlog za rješavanje problema. (I decided to offer him a suggestion for solving the problem.)
6. Želim da *ponudim* svoje usluge kao prevodilac. (I want to offer my services as a translator.)
7. Oni su bili jako sretni kada su dobili *ponudu* za posao. (They were very happy when they received an offer for a job.)
8. Naša tvrtka će *ponuditi* popust na sve proizvode sljedeći tjedan. (Our company will offer a discount on all products next week.)
9. Molim vas da mi *ponudite* neki prijedlog za obilazak grada. (Please offer me some suggestion for sightseeing in the city.)
10. Očekujemo da će tržište *ponuditi* nove mogućnosti za rast naše tvrtke. (We expect the market to offer new opportunities for the growth of our company.)